    "text": "Rare photos of the City of the Dead \ud83d\ude27 Just outside of the village Dargavs (Russia), there is a medieval burial ground holding the remains over 10,000 people. Its history is surrounded by a mystery, and while people aren\u2019t sure when it was first built, it certainly remained a beautiful memorial over the centuries with its curved-roofed crypts.   \ud83d\udccdDargavs, Russia  \ud83c\uddf7\ud83c\uddfa #discoverRussia   1,2,4,5,6,7,8,9 by @mikhoshka  3 by @mytravelteam.ru",
